    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a 
        href="tel:+201234567890"
        class="bg-[#C6A75E] hover:bg-[#b8954f] transition px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-white"
      >
        اتصل بنا الآن
      </a>

      <a 
        href="#contact-form"
        class="border border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold"
